\log(1-x) \leq -x
x \in (0,1)
\log \left(\prod_{i=1}^n (1-\frac a i) \right) = \sum_{i=1}^n \log(1 - \frac a i) \leq \sum_{i=1}^n - \frac a i \underset{n \to \infty}{\longrightarrow} - \infty.
